123
00:05:40,151 --> 00:05:43,164
The Progressive Party of Maldives or PPM.

124
00:05:43,164 --> 00:05:46,118
The President was Abdulla Yameen Abdul Gayoom.

125
00:05:46,118 --> 00:05:47,826
