217
00:09:37,437 --> 00:09:40,139
Politicians were also giving hateful speeches

218
00:09:40,139 --> 00:09:43,046
to end India's presence from their islands.

219
00:09:43,046 --> 00:09:45,659
Seeing all this, the Indian High Commission in Maldives

220
00:09:45,659 --> 00:09:48,845
wrote to the Ministry of Foreign Affairs of Maldives

221
00:09:48,845 --> 00:09:52,108
stating that the articles and social media posts

222
00:09:52,108 --> 00:09:54,234
were attacking Indian dignity.

223
00:09:54,234 --> 00:09:55,540
They asked the ministry to do something about them.

224
00:09:55,540 --> 00:09:58,547
This letter was leaked to Maldives' media.

225
00:09:58,547 --> 00:10:01,305
On 2nd July 2021, the MDP government

226
00:10:01,305 --> 00:10:03,541
officially apologises to India.

227
00:10:03,541 --> 00:10:05,273
And expresses concern that

228
00:10:05,273 --> 00:10:07,560
some people who are spreading hatred against India

229
00:10:07,560 --> 00:10:09,879
on Maldivian media and social media.

230
00:10:09,879 --> 00:10:10,727
Acknowledging it as wrong.

231
00:10:10,727 --> 00:10:13,889
Here, a local news publication DRS was mentioned

232
00:10:13,889 --> 00:10:16,225
with their co-founder Ahmed Azaan.

233
00:10:16,225 --> 00:10:18,239
Specifically, pointing out that

234
00:10:18,239 --> 00:10:21,896
they are the people spreading Anti-India hate.

235
00:10:21,896 --> 00:10:24,825
Regarding India Out slogans, Ahmed Azaan gave a statement

236
00:10:24,825 --> 00:10:30,958
that the campaign does not mean that they 
want to expel the Indians from Maldives.

237
00:10:30,958 --> 00:10:33,411
They do want Indians to be safe in their country.

238
00:10:33,411 --> 00:10:35,540
And that the India Out movement means that

239
00:10:35,540 --> 00:10:37,849
they want to expel the Indian military from their country.

240
00:10:37,849 --> 00:10:40,670
And that the people using the India Out campaign

241
00:10:40,670 --> 00:10:43,001
to threaten the Indians

242
00:10:43,001 --> 00:10:45,558
and to attack Indians

243
00:10:45,558 --> 00:10:46,696
are in the wrong.

244
00:10:46,696 --> 00:10:49,856
He called it an issue-based movement.

245
00:10:49,856 --> 00:10:51,255
So the point is

246
00:10:51,255 --> 00:10:52,798
if this is an issue-based movement,

247
00:10:52,798 --> 00:10:54,173
then what are their issues?

248
